      directAnswer: { question: `How much will my investments grow in ${loc}?`, answer: `Investment growth in ${loc} benefits from no capital gains tax, tax-free dividends, and the SRS tax deduction. CPF OA (2.5%) and SA (4.08%) provide risk-free compounding. Our investment calculator accounts for these advantages with ${ty} tax rates and CPF rules.`, snippetType: "paragraph" },
